      <title>麦肯锡准备向美国司法部阿片类药物调查支付至少 5 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mckinsey-poised-to-pay-at-least-500-million-in-doj-opioid-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，麦肯锡公司即将与美国检察官达成协议，将支付至少 5 亿美元，以解决联邦对其过去帮助阿片类药物制造商提高销量的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mckinsey-poised-to-pay-at-least-500-million-in-doj-opioid-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:41:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>100 岁吉米·卡特在佐治亚州为哈里斯投邮寄选票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/jimmy-carter-100-casts-mail-in-ballot-for-harris-in-georgia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[吉米·卡特现年 100 岁，是美国有史以来最年长的前总统。周三，他参加了 2024 年大选的投票，实现了家人所说的目标，即活得足够长，为副总统卡马拉·哈里斯投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/jimmy-carter-100-casts-mail-in-ballot-for-harris-in-georgia</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:30:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
