      <title>Ukrenergo 经理因泄密面临 8 年监禁，俄罗斯称赞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ukrenergo-manager-faces-8-years-in-jail-for-leaks-russia-praise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰电网运营商的一名经理因涉嫌泄露机密信息和为俄罗斯的袭击辩护而被拘留，面临长达八年的监禁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/ukrenergo-manager-faces-8-years-in-jail-for-leaks-russia-praise</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 17:10:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对党领导人呼吁全国罢课以抗议选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mozambique-opposition-leader-calls-for-national-strike-over-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对派政治家维南西奥·蒙德拉纳 (Venâncio Mondlane) 在 10 月 9 日举行的莫桑比克总统选举的早期计票结果中排名第二，他呼吁周一全国罢选，抗议他已经拒绝的初步结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/mozambique-opposition-leader-calls-for-national-strike-over-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 16:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>魁北克部长称资本利得税上调不会阻碍投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/capital-gains-tax-hike-won-t-deter-investment-quebec-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[魁北克财政部长表示，加拿大提高资本利得税纳入税率是“合理的”，不会阻碍投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/capital-gains-tax-hike-won-t-deter-investment-quebec-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士不会执行欧盟对俄罗斯子公司的制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/swiss-won-t-implement-the-eu-s-russia-sanctions-on-subsidiaries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士决定不全面执行欧盟对俄罗斯的最新制裁措施，称瑞士法律已经允许对总部位于该国的公司的子公司采取措施进行起诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-16/swiss-won-t-implement-the-eu-s-russia-sanctions-on-subsidiaries</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 16 Oct 2024 16:11:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
